 app, or custom code. Without them, your store is invisible to a significant portion of AI search queries."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What is GEO and how is it different from SEO?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"GEO (Generative Engine Optimisation) refers to optimising content to be cited and referenced by AI-powered answer engines like ChatGPT, Perplexity, Claude, and Google's AI Overviews. Unlike traditional SEO which focuses on ranking positions, GEO focuses on making your content the authoritative answer that AI systems cite. Key tactics include structured data, direct factual statements, and content that answers specific questions concisely."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is chat support like Tidio important for AI readiness?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Live chat and chatbot tools like Tidio improve AI readiness indirectly by capturing intent data from customers, providing FAQ content that can be structured, and improving engagement metrics that signal content quality to AI systems. For direct AI readiness, the bigger priorities are structured data and content quality."}}]},{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"BreadcrumbList","itemListElement":[{"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"name":"Home","item":"https://stackarchitect.xyz"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":2,"name":"Tools","item":"https://stackarchitect.xyz/tools/"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":3,"name":"Shopify Agentic Storefront Readiness Checker","item":"https://stackarchitect.xyz/shopify-agentic-storefront-readiness-checker/"}]}];

